What is Venmo?

As you may know, it is a mobile payment app created and owned by PayPal. With a Venmo account, users can transfer funds to others via a mobile phone app.

The users should be United State based because it does work internationally as you can use the app anywhere but you can only link US mobile numbers and US bank accounts. You cannot sign up for a Venmo account being outside of the United States.

Venmo is a good cc cashout method 2023; you can withdraw up to 3000 in USD every week from Venmo if you understand the procedures.
